ERP SYSTEM PROJECT OVERVIEW

Project Name:
ERP Portal Using JSP

Description:
A web-based ERP Portal developed using Java Server Pages (JSP) that provides role-based authentication and separate dashboards for administrators and students.

Modules:

1. Login Module
- User authentication
- Role-based access control
- Session management

2. Admin Module
- View student information
- Manage administrative functions
- Dashboard overview

3. Student Module
- View attendance
- View grades
- Access personal dashboard

Technologies Used:
- Java
- JSP
- HTML
- CSS

Future Enhancements:
- MySQL Database Integration
- CRUD Operations
- Faculty Management
- Attendance Management
- Fee Management
- Report Generation

